name: Cube Goes Weee
description: This game, no, it is not a game, this "masterpiece" is a retrospective of its creator (me), and it talks about an empty white square that promises to get the best times on each map? ... look is not so difficult, you are a square, you can jump things and you must reach the end before time runs out, it is my first game and I hope you have fun, ah and leave a comment if you want :D.
